<template>
  <button id="delete" type="button" @click="openForm"  class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-toggle="modal" :data-bs-target=modalId>
    Brisanje naloga
  </button>
  <request-for-deleting-account-modal></request-for-deleting-account-modal>
</template>

<script>
import $ from "jquery";
import RequestForDeletingAccountModal from "@/components/RequestForDeletingAccountModal";

export default {
  name: "deleteAccountDialog",
  components: {RequestForDeletingAccountModal},
  props:["index","header"],
  created:
      function () {
        this.modalId = "#"+this.index;
      },
methods:{
    openForm(){
      console.log("forma");
      $('#'+this.index).modal('show');
    }
  },
  data(){
    return{
      modalId:""
    }
  }
}

</script>

<style scoped>
#delete{
float:right;
  margin-right:155px;
}
</style>
